om\": 513, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"boat\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"all accounts\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unclear up to late Friday as to what motivated the saboteurs.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"late Friday\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"the saboteurs\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there is no shortage of fanatics with causes; be they part of mainstream or fringe movements.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no shortage\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"fanatics\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"causes\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"mainstream or fringe movements\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, yesterday's attack on the French rail network triggered thoughts of the potential for much, much worse.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.8826496169717803, \"rank\": 0.08764463062745095, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"yesterday's attack\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"thoughts\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Inevitably, memories were cast back to the so-called Munich Massacre at the 1972 Olympics in Munich, Germany.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Munich Massacre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich